Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.actions

Class BuildAction

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.actions.BuildAction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Action
public class BuildAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Action
This class implements Action interface and represents actions in which a worker builds something on a targetCell. It is immutable.
